                    },
                    "body": "This issue should be fixed for the incubator HTTP client.\n\nIn the mean time, since it's a very simple fix (normally I wouldn't bother about the old client) I tried to apply your patch to the old client but could not reproduce the problem with the URL you sent, so I could not test very well.\n\nSince the patch seems to work, I'm applying it. Please test this as soon as you can and let me know if there's still a problem.\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=shahar",
                        "name": "shahar",
                        "displayName": "Shahar Evron",
